      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JUST EMMA (1) hit the ground running and never headed to claim a maiden victory two back then finished a 1.3 lengths third last start at this track over 390m (22.37). Back to track where she won her maiden. Expected to feature in the finish again. BYE BYE SWEETIE (2) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when sixth at Taree Super Track over 300m behind Mulwee Princess (18.28) in a Grade 5. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Expected to run well. TRAVELLING DEAN (8) finds it hard to break through. Finished third (22.41) at this track last time making it four minors on end. Overdue and is among the main hopes. ORIGINALITY (7) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
